blackhole-threats (1.0.0-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial package release for the blackhole-threats RTBH route server.
  * Package the daemon with systemd integration, packaged defaults, and the
    reference example configuration.
  * Install the blackhole-threats(8) manual page and support immediate feed
    refresh through `systemctl reload blackhole-threats`.
  * Embed build metadata in source and package builds and validate the package
    on Debian trixie.

